     {
         "title": "Shinkansen trial of moderately air conditioned cars draws mixed reactions from travellers",
         "description": "Some passengers are grateful for the warmer carriages, while others say they\u0026#8217;re the last thing Japan needs during an excruciatingly hot summer. One of the unique quirks of train travel in Japan is the ability to hop on a moderately air-conditioned carriage. These carriages, which have the air conditioning set at a higher temperature than [\u0026#8230;]",
         "content": "\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-738975\" src=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-2.jpeg?w=640\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-2.jpeg 1600w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-2.jpeg?resize=150,100 150w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-2.jpeg?resize=640,426 640w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-2.jpeg?resize=768,512 768w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-2.jpeg?resize=1024,682 1024w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-2.jpeg?resize=1536,1023 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: large\"\u003eSome passengers are grateful for the warmer carriages, while others say they\u0026#8217;re the last thing Japan needs during an excruciatingly hot summer.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-738956\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOne of the unique quirks of train travel in Japan is \u003cstrong\u003ethe ability to hop on a moderately air-conditioned carriage\u003c/strong\u003e. These carriages, \u003cstrong\u003ewhich have the air conditioning set at a higher temperature than the rest of the train\u003c/strong\u003e, are commonly found on a number of commuter railways across Japan, offering a more comfortable environment for passengers who are sensitive to cold air.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhile the practice has generally been limited to everyday commuter trains, where it first appeared in the ‘80s, \u003cstrong\u003ethe Shinkansen is now trialling its own moderately air-conditioned cars, but not everyone is happy about it\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe trial began on 1 July and is set to run until 31 August on\u003cstrong\u003e some 16-car Hikari services operating on the Tokaido and Sanyo Shinkansen lines,\u003c/strong\u003e which together connect Tokyo with Hakata in Fukuoka, passing through major cities including \u003cstrong\u003eNagoya\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eKyoto\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eOsaka\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eHiroshima\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: center\"\u003e▼ The Tokaido Shinkansen, run by JR Central, links Tokyo to Shin-Osaka, while the Sanyo Shinkansen, run by JR West, continues from Shin-Osaka to Hakata.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-738977\" src=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-route-Japan-Tokyo-to-osaka-kyoto-.jpeg?w=640\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"612\" srcset=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-route-Japan-Tokyo-to-osaka-kyoto-.jpeg 900w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-route-Japan-Tokyo-to-osaka-kyoto-.jpeg?resize=150,144 150w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-route-Japan-Tokyo-to-osaka-kyoto-.jpeg?resize=640,612 640w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-route-Japan-Tokyo-to-osaka-kyoto-.jpeg?resize=768,735 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe trial is currently limited to one carriage, Car No. 3, which is an unreserved carriage. In this car, the air-conditioning is set around 2 degrees Celsius (3.6 degrees Fahrenheit) warmer than the rest of the train.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: center\"\u003e▼ The trial was announced earlier this year.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cblockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-lang=\"en\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-partner=\"jetpack\"\u003e\u003cp lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e東海道・山陽新幹線『弱冷房車』の試験導入についてのお知らせ\u003cbr\u003e2026年7⽉1⽇〜8月31⽇、東海道・⼭陽新幹線では16両編成のひかり号3号⾞（⾃由席）にて、弱冷房⾞を試験導⼊いたします。詳細は以下のリンクをご確認ください。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e■リンク先\u003ca href=\"https://t.co/DElaKpt0pv\"\u003ehttps://t.co/DElaKpt0pv\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://t.co/TqpBWP0Px9\"\u003epic.twitter.com/TqpBWP0Px9\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u0026mdash; 東海道新幹線（東京～新大阪）運行情報【ＪＲ東海公式】 (@JRC_Shinkan_jp) \u003ca href=\"https://x.com/JRC_Shinkan_jp/status/2057728402619248901?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\"\u003eMay 22, 2026\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNow that the trial is underway, railway operators JR Central and JR West are monitoring passenger demand and collecting feedback through onboard surveys. According to comments on social media though, not everyone is happy about the service, with some people saying the warmer carriage felt far too hot for this time of year, while others argued that bullet trains should introduce carriages with stronger air conditioning instead, to provide more relief from the intense heat.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-738974\" src=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-.jpeg?w=640\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-.jpeg 1600w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-.jpeg?resize=150,100 150w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-.jpeg?resize=640,427 640w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-.jpeg?resize=768,512 768w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-.jpeg?resize=1024,683 1024w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-.jpeg?resize=1536,1024 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMany, however, wondered why the railways had chosen the hottest time of year to trial weaker air conditioning.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAccording to JR Central, the trial was prompted by passenger feedback, with surveys revealing there was genuine demand from travellers who find standard Shinkansen air conditioning to be uncomfortably cold. JR Central also said \u003ca href=\"https://soranews24.com/2025/07/01/japan-railways-to-test-weak-air-conditioning-in-some-shinkansen-cars-this-summer/\"\u003ea smaller trial conducted last summer\u003c/a\u003e produced encouraging results, prompting the companies to expand both the number of trains involved and the length of the trial this year.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe companies chose to conduct the trial in an unreserved carriage so passengers can choose whether or not to use it and easily move to another carriage if they find it too warm or too cold.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-738976\" src=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-3.jpeg?w=640\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-3.jpeg 1600w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-3.jpeg?resize=150,100 150w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-3.jpeg?resize=640,427 640w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-3.jpeg?resize=768,512 768w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-3.jpeg?resize=1024,683 1024w, https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2026/07/Shinkansen-Japan-weak-air-conditioning-car-unreserved-seating-travel-carriage-railway-company-trial-travel-Sanyo-Tokaido-Hikari-Tokyo-Kyoto-Osaka-news-3.jpeg?resize=1536,1024 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAmong the many complaints, however, there were some passengers who welcomed the warmer conditions, saying standard Shinkansen air conditioning can become uncomfortably cold during longer journeys. Others were pleased to finally have a carriage where they could travel without feeling the chill.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eJR Central says train crews already adjust temperatures according to conditions inside each train, but acknowledges that comfort is subjective and no single temperature will satisfy everyone on board. Passengers who do find themselves feeling uncomfortable are encouraged to flag their concerns with onboard staff, who can offer suggestions and make adjustments where possible, depending on onboard conditions.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eSource: \u003ca href=\"https://jr-central.co.jp/news/release/_pdf/000045595.pdf\"\u003eJR Central\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/93a3c32a322758e8fd0c2316d9373a0993a14904\"\u003eYahoo! Japan News\u003c/a\u003e via \u003ca href=\"http://blog.esuteru.com/archives/10545913.html\"\u003eHachima Kikou\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eFeatured image: \u003ca href=\"https://www.pakutaso.com/20150401114post-1.html\"\u003ePakutaso\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eInsert images: \u003ca href=\"https://global.jr-central.co.jp/en/info/timetable/\"\u003eCentral Japan Railway Company\u003c/a\u003e, Pakutaso (\u003ca href=\"https://www.pakutaso.com/20230349072post-45742.html\"\u003e1\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.pakutaso.com/20230356072post-45745.html\"\u003e2\u003c/a\u003e)\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cem\u003e● Want to hear about SoraNews24\u0026#8217;s latest articles as soon as they\u0026#8217;re published? \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RocketNews24En\"\u003eFollow us on Facebook\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://twitter.com/RocketNews24En\"\u003eTwitter\u003c/a\u003e!\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n",
